Python project to download YouTube video from command line and 
generate an mp3 file for personal use in audio playback devices.

mp3it Author: Chosen1, Twitter: @chosen1x
YouTap Author: Sundar Srinivasan, Twitter: @krishnasun

Usage: python mp3it.py "<link-to-youtube-video-page>"

License under: Apache License, Version: 2.0
	(http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html)

The reason for giving the link in double-quotes is that sometimes the link 
contains '&'(ampersand), which the UNIX interprets as "run the program in background"
